282
00:14:41,762 --> 00:14:43,962
What? We have to go out?

283
00:14:45,262 --> 00:14:47,462
You can come in

284
00:14:47,462 --> 00:14:48,962
after Officer Takagi finishes what he has to say.

285
00:14:48,962 --> 00:14:50,162
Officer Takagi?

286
00:14:50,162 --> 00:14:52,462
Oh, hey, where's Conan...

287
00:14:55,362 --> 00:14:57,362
Oh, that's right.

288
00:14:59,462 --> 00:15:01,762
Please allow me to explain.

289
00:15:01,762 --> 00:15:04,662
The key to this case

290
00:15:04,662 --> 00:15:06,862
is indeed the box locked with a key.

291
00:15:06,862 --> 00:15:09,262
Mr. Kasuga, the food coordinator locked

292
00:15:09,262 --> 00:15:12,662
the box filled with fruit with the padlock

293
00:15:12,662 --> 00:15:14,762
and sent it to the TV station.

294
00:15:14,762 --> 00:15:19,462
Next, the producer Mr. Taruoka instructs Mr. Furuya, the AD

295
00:15:19,462 --> 00:15:22,062
