296
00:15:22,062 --> 00:15:25,862
and send it back to Mr. Kasuga.

297
00:15:25,862 --> 00:15:30,262
Then Mr. Kasuga removes the padlock that he locked

298
00:15:30,262 --> 00:15:32,662
and sends it back to the TV station again

299
00:15:32,662 --> 00:15:36,862
and was stored in the storage room.

300
00:15:36,862 --> 00:15:38,162
But then, why the corpse of Mr. Takegi

301
00:15:38,162 --> 00:15:41,062
was found inside the box

302
00:15:41,062 --> 00:15:43,362
