381
00:19:56,862 --> 00:19:59,462
Where do you have such evidence?

382
00:19:59,462 --> 00:20:01,562
The evidence is...

383
00:20:01,562 --> 00:20:03,862
In your stomach, Mr. AD.

384
00:20:03,862 --> 00:20:04,962
Huh?

385
00:20:04,962 --> 00:20:08,762
Mr. AD, after you put that man into the box,

386
00:20:08,762 --> 00:20:10,062
you drank up about ten juiced apples

387
00:20:10,062 --> 00:20:12,262
because there wasn't enough space to put him inside, right?

388
00:20:12,262 --> 00:20:13,262
You did this by using the little prop juice mixer

389
00:20:13,262 --> 00:20:16,262
