390
00:20:16,262 --> 00:20:19,162
After all, the footage of the surveillance camera

391
00:20:19,162 --> 00:20:20,662
shows that you weren't holding anything

392
00:20:20,662 --> 00:20:22,262
when you came out of storage room.

393
00:20:24,162 --> 00:20:25,962
Even if it were so,

394
00:20:25,962 --> 00:20:28,062
it's already digested in my stomach.

395
00:20:28,062 --> 00:20:29,762
Don't you know?

396
00:20:31,062 --> 00:20:32,562
There is a substance in the seed of apples

397
00:20:32,562 --> 00:20:35,462
called amygdalin,

398
00:20:35,462 --> 00:20:37,362
and over eating it can cause problems, you know?

399
00:20:38,762 --> 00:20:41,762
Mr. AD, when you put the apples in the juice mixer,

400
00:20:41,762 --> 00:20:44,462
