404
00:20:54,662 --> 00:20:57,362
But, if you haven't eaten anything from morning,

405
00:20:57,362 --> 00:20:59,462
I'm sure you haven't moved your bowels yet.

406
00:20:59,462 --> 00:21:01,962
So, I think it'll come out in time,

407
00:21:01,962 --> 00:21:03,762
